<sec xml:base="/std/iso/81286/en/chunks/id-d1540810-0da6-4530-94e3-ab30ee43c8ae.xml" id="id-f6f0f658-5d42-4d26-8efd-a338d500ab40"><title><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="deann.desai@gatech.edu" change-id="3653d6de-adee-44c1-8f3f-9b68c2e39791" timestamp="1627659718547"?>Basic items for SMS<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="3653d6de-adee-44c1-8f3f-9b68c2e39791"?></title><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="deann.desai@gatech.edu" change-id="99f8e2cf-72e4-4a6a-84f7-4c314f0141da" timestamp="1628092503930"?>Basic items for SMS reflect requirements related to structure in <std id="id-d3593914-6074-47ae-a7ca-03fa8dda9884"><std-id std-id-link-type="urn" std-id-type="undated">iso:pub:std:DIS:69426</std-id><std-ref>ISO 50001</std-ref></std><?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="99f8e2cf-72e4-4a6a-84f7-4c314f0141da"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="571844" change-id="3f635d41-5ab4-4ca3-d9fe-80ab7555263e" text="ISO 50001" timestamp="1633356058291"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="deann.desai@gatech.edu" change-id="2e37e602-ef3c-4ae6-85ba-f3f0df36fdfa" timestamp="1628092503930"?>. The basic items are described in <xref as:rid="chunks/id-d1540810-0da6-4530-94e3-ab30ee43c8ae.xml#id-9e223a63-e338-44e6-a90c-45dbc2adab97" ref-type="table" id="id-7e84f9bb-e907-41cf-b7a5-a0308bb4981c" xmlns:as="http://niso-sts-authoring-solution/authoring-schema"><?fontoxml-text-placeholder text="type the link text"?></xref>.</p><non-normative-note><p>The score for each item related to structure improving the organizations’ energy performance directly is two points and the score of other items is one point.</p></non-normative-note><p>The organization should evaluate their EnMS according to the basic items for SMS. To conduct the evaluation the organization should assess if the organization’s EnMS has attained each evaluation criteria item. When the EnMS attains the item, the organization gets a score for that item. After checking all items in <xref as:rid="chunks/id-d1540810-0da6-4530-94e3-ab30ee43c8ae.xml#id-9e223a63-e338-44e6-a90c-45dbc2adab97" ref-type="table" id="id-d2f40a00-22ab-41e4-8ca1-4c42ff8b40ce" xmlns:as="http://niso-sts-authoring-solution/authoring-schema"><?fontoxml-text-placeholder text="type the link text"?></xref>, the score for basic SMS items is calculated using the total score of all attained items.</p><table-wrap id="id-9e223a63-e338-44e6-a90c-45dbc2adab97"><caption><title>Basic Items for SMS</title></caption><table><col width="20%"/><col width="20%"/><col width="20%"/><col width="20%"/><col width="20%"/><thead><tr><th align="center" valign="middle" style="border-top-style: solid; border-top-width: 4px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-width: 4px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 4px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-width: 4px;"><p><bold>Serial No.</bold></p></th><th align="center" valign="middle" style="border-top-style: solid; border-top-width: 4px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-width: 4px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 4px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-width: 4px;"><p><bold>Clause number in</bold></p><p/></th><th colspan="2" align="center" valign="middle" style="border-top-style: solid; border-top-width: 4px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-width: 4px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 4px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-width: 4px;"><p><bold>Evaluation criteria</bold></p><p><italic>(description of the reference state)</italic></p></th><th align="center" valign="middle" style="border-top-style: solid; border-top-width: 4px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-width: 4px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 4px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-width: 4px;"><p><bold>Maximum possible Score</bold></p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td rowspan="2" align="center" valign="middle" style="border-top-style: solid; border-top-width: 4px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-width: 4p